window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>An essential companion to the Third Heaven novels&nbsp;</p> <p>At the end&nbsp;of&nbsp;<i>The Third Heaven Apocalypse&nbsp;of&nbsp;Kings</i>, Henel James was invited to discover more about the journalistic Grigori.&nbsp;</p> <p>Why has the reporter been summoned to Heaven? What would Argoth the Prince&nbsp;of&nbsp;House Grigori want?&nbsp;</p> <p>This original story from Donovan M. Neal expands on earlier events that helped shape the angelic-world&nbsp;of&nbsp;the Third Heaven Universe, with some surprising nods to the Third Heaven stories that will delight fans&nbsp;of&nbsp;the books.&nbsp;</p> <p>Return to the realm&nbsp;of&nbsp;angels, to the time before time: a time before the rise&nbsp;of&nbsp;fallen stars, and explore the realm&nbsp;of&nbsp;Limbo...the realm where all your choices live and from which no one can escape.&nbsp;</p> <p>Listen to the first book&nbsp;of&nbsp;this exciting new series now.</p>"; 
